snippet.title: Cloud 9 Blessings
snippet.description:
Welcome to Cloud 9 Blessings! This channel is about sharing the good news of our Lord and Savior Yeshua Hamashiach, Jesus Christ. The goal is to enlighten our followers by sharing Rapture dreams, Visions , Near Death Experiences & encouraging one another with Scripture. Shalom!

If you can find it in your heart & would like to help and support Cloud9blessings, it would be greatly appreciated! Your support helps me to continue the ministry as well as create videos!

Thank You all so much and God Bless!


Cash App : $Cloud9bless 

http://venmo.com/Cloud9blessings

Visit our Website http://Cloud9blessings.com


1 Thessalonians 4

For the Lord himself shall descend from heaven with a shout, with the voice of the archangel, and with the trump of God: and the dead in Christ shall rise first: then we which are alive and remain shall be caught up together with them in the clouds, to meet the Lord in the air: and so shall we ever be with the Lord. Wherefore comfort one another with these words.
